Demonic_Text: nip on right cheek below ear
with a rough (ruch) man all black
said the devil offered him god
leflt leg, between her shoulders, up her 'hensh'
said she refused to do this
foot on a cloth on the floor
this was implied by the prosecution
she sat down on her Knees
back side of left arm below the elbow
on the viens and sinews of her leg.
right side of her nose under her eye
when a black dog lay with her in bed
tried to name her Jeane, she said no
his body was hard and cold
right shoulder, left shoulder and her heave
in the middle of the floor
